# Generated example outputs
examples/*.csv
examples/*.html
examples/*.toml
*.html

# Notebook rendered output — sources live at examples/notebooks/*.md.
# `make notebooks` writes everything into gallery/:
#   gallery/<name>.md           committed → GitHub-browseable Markdown
#   gallery/plots/<name>/*.svg  committed → referenced by .md inline
#   gallery/<name>.html         ignored   → bulky Plotly bundles, local view
#   gallery/index.html          ignored   → generated index for the HTML build
# The carve-outs below override the global *.svg and *.html rules for the
# gallery's committed assets.
gallery/*.html
!gallery/
!gallery/**/*.svg
